thread.title: Jerry Sanders
thread.title_full: Matboard and More reviewed by Jerry Sanders

author: Jerry Sanders
title: Jerry Sanders
text: These mats are cut to the best industry standards. Shipping was timely and well packaged for shipment. The best news, depending on number of mats ordered, I paid less than half frame shop prices for 10 double oval mats. Communication was also very good.
